IT CHANGED
MY FAMILY.

867
01:40:24,885 --> 01:40:28,555
IT CHANGED
EVERYTHING.

868
01:40:28,655 --> 01:40:31,058
YOU LIVE
DAY BY DAY,

869
01:40:31,158 --> 01:40:35,062
AND THEY'RE ALWAYS
IN YOUR MIND.

870
